00:23:08,902 --> 00:23:10,683
Getting into the forums and spending an afternoon

472
00:23:10,803 --> 00:23:13,664
quelling player concerns resulted in a 54% increase

473
00:23:13,744 --> 00:23:14,825
in week over week revenue.

474
00:23:15,785 --> 00:23:18,266
It seems hard to believe, and trust me, it was,

