00:23:18,906 --> 00:23:21,547
but we weren't running any new sales or interesting events

476
00:23:21,607 --> 00:23:23,228
or anything like that during these spikes.

477
00:23:23,848 --> 00:23:25,929
The conclusion to tie to this is that spending the time

478
00:23:25,969 --> 00:23:27,389
to actually connect to your players

479
00:23:27,489 --> 00:23:29,370
means that you might be making your company more money.

480
00:23:30,231 --> 00:23:31,731
If there was ever a reason to bring to your company

481
00:23:31,771 --> 00:23:34,412
how important having a community team is, this is it.

482
00:23:37,133 --> 00:23:37,873
So let's recap.

483
00:23:38,354 --> 00:23:40,255
What can you do to maintain player enthusiasm

484
00:23:40,295 --> 00:23:41,616
and help mitigate frustrations?

485
00:23:43,156 --> 00:23:44,357
Champion those who are passionate,

486
00:23:44,477 --> 00:23:46,679
